Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.93,0:21:22.89,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}In spite of how the world decides to see my life
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.41,0:21:27.12,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(400,400)}Would I still have a chance for us to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:33.41,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(400,400)}Over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.81,0:21:40.89,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}If I decide to burn instead of fading out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.29,0:21:44.89,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}I still would like the chance for us to say good bye
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.89,0:21:52.27,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:56.79,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}If we can be found, we sure can get lost
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.93,0:22:01.23,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,400)}Through all the madness of falling in love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:07.31,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\an7}{\fad(200,0)}If we're truly lost, I don't want to be found here dying alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.31,0:22:09.67,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,400)}Virtually lost, don't wanna be found here dying alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.95,0:22:14.81,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}The stain of RED that colors the pavement
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:18.77,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Painted with blood of somebody you love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.07,0:22:23.63,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,400)}Is this sacrifice for the broken
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:28.61,JP - ed,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,600)}Losing the purest of what's in your heart
